wmInfo - Public Release
--------------------------------------------------------------
Authors...:	Robert Kling

Description
--------------------------------------------------------------
wmInfo is a dockapp that can display text-format information.
You use a plugin that writes to stdout and wmInfo will capture
the output and display it row by row.

Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------
wmwinfo -h to print the switches. A couple of plugins named
<something>.wmiplugin should have come with the tarball.
Note that the plugins need NOT have the extension wmiplugin
and need NOT to be shell-scripts.

